    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方Q群：715026848（1）625951216（2）</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >###预警###</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本游戏包含强烈刺激的内容。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>部分路线含有血腥暴力、身体裸露等画面以及描写。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>**本游戏仍然存在<u>纯爱路线</u>。请谨慎做出每一项选择。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/4886b76759b139348ead14451347391b.avif?t=1771076581\" width=600 height=130 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你”因为疑似患上<strong>精神传染病</strong>被父母<strong>送进医院</strong>。医院对你进行前置治疗和观察后，确诊后决定挑选“你”为新治疗法的<strong>临床实验</strong>体，进行定期治疗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >医生为你带来一个无比美丽的年轻男性——不，<strong><u>男性人形机器人</u></strong>？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/8c108807abd4ed5579f32c37dc1a23fc.avif?t=1771076581\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras_big/8c108807abd4ed5579f32c37dc1a23fc.avif?t=1771076581 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你”需要使用<strong>机器人治病</strong>，并且保持<strong>精神稳定</strong>为研究所提供数据。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是……第一个体验项目怎么是？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/8467567277d48a1d585c9b0a1a6904ad.poster.avif?t=1771076581\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/8467567277d48a1d585c9b0a1a6904ad.webm?t=1771076581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/8467567277d48a1d585c9b0a1a6904ad.mp4?t=1771076581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/4391ce5f4dd0ff8d53b6110bedcc80d0.avif?t=1771076581\" width=600 height=130 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >医院的实验疗法是让和机器人<strong>【互动】</strong>。你可以自由选择各种<strong><u>治疗【项目】</u></strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >温柔的肌肤接触、原始的物理惩罚。医院为你提供了<strong><u>几十种</u></strong>治疗项目。机器人对不同治疗的接受度也会随着你的行为慢慢改变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>六种</strong>不同的治疗风格你可以任意选择——<u>人类、机械、配合、爱慕、痛感、反抗</u>。不要一次太激进，掌握治疗规律，循序渐进对病情更有帮助。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/d9417c1498433ee3570d8d911bae7e26.avif?t=1771076581\" width=600 height=130 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >医院每天日程分为早中晚三段时间。你可以选择用机器人治疗、休息、提交数据、完成医嘱……记住，<strong>无休止的索求</strong>偶尔也需要按下暂停键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>麻木的感官</strong>也许短暂抽离后会<strong>放大刺激</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙运用各种<strong>道具</strong>，让精神回复变得更有效率和味道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/3d7196e9b2d97eefa5fa9f52751bba00.avif?t=1771076581\" width=616 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你也可以为机器人换上特殊的衣服，封闭的医院生活也许需要一点色彩~❤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/abf684c1e6312a3df52902544482f81b.poster.avif?t=1771076581\" width=602 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/abf684c1e6312a3df52902544482f81b.webm?t=1771076581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/abf684c1e6312a3df52902544482f81b.mp4?t=1771076581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——只要在医院规则内，你可以自由【行动】。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>夜晚熄灯时间与机器人的<strong>偷偷互动</strong>，医生并没有制止你……</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/ea3eb3b2aedae0e7deb9d9352dc2ba74.poster.avif?t=1771076581\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/ea3eb3b2aedae0e7deb9d9352dc2ba74.webm?t=1771076581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/ea3eb3b2aedae0e7deb9d9352dc2ba74.mp4?t=1771076581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126170/extras/4cbfe3404277f3ffa59df77fbad6ed80.avif?t=1771076581\" width=600 height=130 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着治疗日程继续，选择不同的治疗方案以及对医院的态度。你会进入不同的剧情和治 疗养成路线，最终获得不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的每一个选择、每一次治疗都至关重要。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请认真对待你的病症，配合医院治疗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>————————患者，你准备好了吗？请立刻入院。</strong></p>",
